== About ==

The EmbedVideo extension is used to embed flash videos from video hosting sites
such as YouTube.com into a MediaWiki wiki website. It adds a parser function
{{#ev:}} which can be added to pages to embed videos in line with other content.

For more information about EmbedVideo, to download, to contribute, and to report
bugs and problems, visit the GitHub project page:

    http://www.github.com/whiteknight/mediawiki-embedvideo


== License ==

